Maijoor Says OTC Derivatives Market Should Be Under Supervision

-- B y   A n a b e l a   R e i s
-- 
2011-10-13T14:37:36Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-13/maijoor-says-otc-derivatives-market-should-be-under-supervision.html
Steven Maijoor, chairman of the
European Securities and Markets Authority, said the over-the-
counter derivatives market should be supervised and more
transparent. He spoke at a conference in Lisbon today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Anabela Reis in Lisbon at 
